lead_paragraph: Shaun Marsh will miss the remainder of Australia's tour of Sri Lanka after the top-order batsman broke a finger while fielding during Sunday's third one-day international, the country's cricket board has said.

headline.print_headline: Finger Break Ends Sri Lanka Tour for Australia's Marsh
